{"tid":327040,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"考試考得唔好 老豆打到老母仆街 點算","createTime":"2017-07-18T12:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T16:03:08.000Z","uid":129222,"like":13,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1232499b36edf6169ee65cb042b320f756d1a320","tid":327040,"uid":129222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T12:42:15.000Z","msg":"是咁的 咁早排就考完試<br />\n因為自己心散成日打LOL <br />\n搞到退步左 有幾科所以唔合格 我都知衰架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁放左成績之後我就同左老母講啦 <br />\n老母都無點話我 淨係叫我唔好打咁多機 以後要比心機啲<br />\n咁一路過左成個月都無事<br />\n到左頭先食完飯<br />\n老豆無啦啦問我考成點 問我拎黎睇下啲卷<br />\n咁我比完佢睇之後佢面好黑 <br />\n叫我入房先<br />\n咁我係房到就聽到<br />\n佢問我老母點解唔同佢講<br />\n跟手無啦啦星左佢一巴<br />\n咁我老母就同佢講你成日出去應酬 又唔理個仔 洗咩同你講<br />\n跟手老豆又車多野<br />\n<br />\n而家出面好似火星撞地球咁 點算<br />\n<br />\n利申:升中3"},{"pid":"2c533e2c7907542a92660b39d7b80435cc515efb","tid":327040,"uid":85163,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T12:43:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1701f52d76532e58fb63af64544720c5576cf03","tid":327040,"uid":1020,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T12:44:34.000Z","msg":"老母好錫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e69a21a96a547d50023e5cb53278dcd91153fd","tid":327040,"uid":126436,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T12:44:58.000Z","msg":"打返你老豆 黎個老豆打老母 呀仔在後"},{"pid":"2a5c6acb3311a3baf93fd6353ac6af6b0782d0d4","tid":327040,"uid":2766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T12:45:36.000Z","msg":"個始作俑者係你<br />\n根本你擔心都無補於事<br />\n無你就無呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8891c0cb0d8eb33c60f04fdd93c31b8d62ad617","tid":327040,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T12:45:50.000Z","msg":"報驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c34ac1d5817671822d80e8ccaea0a37bea8e30","tid":327040,"uid":129222,"like":0,"di